                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17190514-6-off29 t17190514-6-cd30"></join>. It appeared the Prosecutor had been making merry with some Friends, but was very sensible and knew what he, did, and going home about 12 a Clock at Night he met the Prisoner and two others in <placeName id="t17190514-6-crimeloc31">Leaden-Hall-Street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17190514-6-crimeloc31" type="placeName" value="Leaden-Hall-Street"></interp>
